ion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Ftaiwan-detects-10-chinese-military-aircraft-five-naval-ships-around-nation%2Farticleshow%2F107390696.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Ftaiwan-detects-10-chinese-military-aircraft-five-naval-ships-around-nation%2Famp_articleshow%2F107390696.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Ftaiwan-detects-10-chinese-military-aircraft-five-naval-ships-around-nation%2Famp_articleshow%2F107390696.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LK%20Advani%3A%20From%20Rath%20Yatra%20to%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20a%20Political%20Journey%20Propelled%20By%20Violence%2C%20Polarisation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03231249%2FRath-yatra-II-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Having%20buried%20him%20in%20the%20shadows%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20retirement%20bench%2C%20redundantly%20named%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emargdarshak%20mandal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20now%20decided%20to%20resurrect%20the%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%20by%20conferring%20him%20with%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20highest%20honour%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdvani%2C%20the%20man%20who%20as%20party%20president%20in%201989%20first%20incorporated%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Ram%20Mandir%20at%20Ayodhya%20as%20one%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20agendas%20in%20its%20Palampur%20National%20Executive%20resolution%2C%20was%20recently%20both%20%E2%80%9Cinvited%20and%20disinvited%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20temple%E2%80%99s%20grand%20consecration%20ceremony%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20could%20not%20have%20been%20a%20more%20suitable%20time%20for%20the%20Hindutva%20ideologue%20to%20receive%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20in%20a%20(new)%20India%20that%20embodies%20widespread%20feelings%20of%20uncertainty%2C%20fear%20and%20insecurity%2C%20the%20very%20foundation%20of%20which%20was%20laid%20by%20none%20other%20than%20Advani.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFated%20to%20watch%20the%20fulfillment%20of%20his%20single-most%20significant%20political%20goal%2C%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20on%20television%20screens%2C%20Advani%20at%2096%20can%20now%20recall%20his%20unparalleled%20role%20in%20driving%20the%20country%20towards%20sharp%20religious%20polarisation%20as%20his%20contributions%20have%20finally%20been%20acknowledged%20by%20his%20greatest%20mentee%20and%20successor%2C%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20decades%2C%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20highest%20honour%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20an%20instrument%20for%20political%20messaging.%20While%20scientists%2C%20musicians%2C%20sportspersons%20and%20social%20reformers%20have%20received%20the%20honour%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20political%20dispensations%20at%20the%20Centre%20have%20mostly%20chosen%20to%20confer%20the%20award%20to%20ideologues%20of%20their%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20none%20may%20be%20as%20polarising%20as%20Advani%2C%20for%20he%20is%20regarded%20as%20a%20divisive%20political%20figure%20in%20his%20own%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20is%20among%20those%20founders%20of%20the%20BJP%20who%20gave%20a%20clear%20and%20sharp%20ideological%20line%20to%20the%20saffron%20party%20from%20his%20days%20in%20the%20Jana%20Sangh%2C%20even%20when%20his%20party%20had%20mostly%20depended%20on%20stitching%20up%20anti-Congress%20alliances.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20perhaps%20played%20the%20biggest%20organisational%20role%20in%20transforming%20the%20saffron%20party%20into%20a%20mass%20organisation%2C%20even%20as%20it%20came%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20communal%20harmony.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22An%20Advani%20Honoured%2C%20the%20Republic%20Diminished%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fan-advani-honoured-the-republic-diminished%5C%22%3EAn%20Advani%20Honoured%2C%20the%20Republic%20Diminished%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20adopting%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20resolution%20in%20Palampur%20to%20piloting%20the%20majoritarian%20narrative%20in%20the%20country%20through%20his%20countrywide%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Erath%20yatra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Advani%20built%20the%20party%20brick-by-brick%20along%20with%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20only%20to%20be%20sidelined%20by%20his%20ideological%20mentors%20in%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20in%20the%20end.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20is%20still%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20longest-serving%20party%20president%2C%20having%20been%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20party%20machinery%20between%201986-91%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20then%20between%201993-98%20and%20finally%20a%20year-long%20stint%20in%202004-05.%20He%20was%20forced%20by%20the%20RSS%20to%20resign%20from%20the%20position%20after%20he%20courted%20controversy%20over%20describing%20Muhammad%20Ali%20Jinnah%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Csecular%E2%80%9D%20leader%2C%20doing%20a%20180-degree%20deviation%20from%20the%20Sangh%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eparivar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20and%20his%20own%20position.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RSS%2C%20which%20had%20forced%20Vajpayee%20to%20appoint%20Advani%20as%20the%20deputy%20prime%20minister%2C%20repositioned%20its%20view%20on%20the%20senior%20leader.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESays%20senior%20journalist%20Neena%20Vyas%2C%20who%20has%20covered%20the%20BJP%20for%20over%2030%20years%3A%20%E2%80%9CAdvani%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20in%202005%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20end%20of%20his%20political%20career.%20Although%20he%20was%20shunted%20out%20only%20in%202013%2C%20the%20BJP%20having%20lost%20the%202009%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20with%20him%20as%20the%20PM%20candidate%2C%20he%20had%20lost%20face%20in%20the%20Sangh%20(parivar)%20ranks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20Modi%2C%20who%20he%20trained%20and%20defended%20all%20his%20life%2C%20ended%20up%20as%20the%20one%20to%20push%20him%20into%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmargdarshak%20mandal%E2%80%9D.%20One%20may%20say%20that%20he%20reaped%20what%20he%20sowed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202004%20Ranchi%20party%20conclave%2C%20Advani%20described%20the%20BJP%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fpolitics%2Farticle30225920.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EChosen%20Instrument%20of%20the%20Divine%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20to%20rule%20India%2C%20in%20an%20immediate%20attempt%20to%20adopt%20hardline%20Hindutva%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20party%20was%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20dynamics%20of%20coalition%20politics%2C%20but%20in%20the%20long%20term%20conceiving%20the%20Indian%20state%20in%20a%20way%20that%20a%20country%20like%20Israel%20defines%20itself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdvani%E2%80%99s%20statement%20as%20party%20president%20was%20perceived%20as%20undermining%20Vajpayee%2C%20who%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20moderate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20then%2C%20Advani%20had%20earned%20himself%20the%20reputation%20of%20being%20an%20arch-rival%20of%20Vajpayee%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20in%20the%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAdvani%20undermined%20Vajpayee%20multiple%20times.%20I%20can%20remember%20how%20he%20and%20his%20cohort%20stumped%20Vajpayee%20by%20scuttling%20the%202001%20Agra%20peace%20summit%20called%20by%20him%2C%20recalls%20Vyas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20the%20Lahore%20Bus%20Yatra%2C%20Pakistan%20started%20the%20Kargil%20War.%20Yet%2C%20Vajpayee%20wanted%20to%20give%20India-Pakistan%20friendship%20a%20chance%20by%20inviting%20Pervez%20Musharraf%20to%20Agra%20for%20talks.%20A%20joint%20statement%20was%20practically%20ready%20but%20was%20undone%20by%20Advani%20and%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20at%20the%20end%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20talks%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-provocateur-in-chief-l-k-advani%5C%22%3EL.K.%20Advani%2C%20the%20Provocateur%20in%20Chief%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20talks%2C%20Advani%20attempted%20to%20belittle%20Vajpayee%20by%20declaring%20a%20policy%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fdecision-soon-on-hot-pursuit-of-terrorists-advani%2Farticleshow%2F64534330.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehot%20pursuit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20of%20terrorists%20across%20the%20Line%20of%20Control.%20Similarly%2C%20Advani%20made%20many%20attempts%20to%20drive%20out%20Brajesh%20Mishra%2C%20Vajpayee%E2%80%99s%20principal%20secretary%20in%20the%20PMO%20and%20the%20then-national%20security%20advisor%2C%20but%20failed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%202009%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20was%20his%20last%20chance%20to%20fulfill%20his%20ambition%20of%20becoming%20prime%20minister%2C%20but%20by%20then%20he%20had%20cultivated%20more%20enemies%20in%20the%20party%20than%20friends%2C%20with%20even%20his%20allies%20like%20Yashwant%20Sinha%20and%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20protesting%20against%20his%20description%20of%20Jinnah%20during%20his%20Pakistan%20visit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20desire%20to%20undercut%20Vajpayee%2C%20Advani%20almost%20staged%20a%20coup%20in%20the%20famous%20Goa%20National%20Executive%20meeting%20in%20April%202002.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFresh%20off%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20anti-Muslim%20riots%2C%20Vajpayee%20had%20almost%20decided%20to%20ask%20the%20then-Gujarat%20chief%20minister%20Modi%20to%20resign.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Vyas%20says%20that%20Advani%20got%20wind%20of%20it%20and%20sent%20Arun%20Jaitley%20to%20Gandhinagar%20to%20stymie%20the%20decision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CJaitley%20came%20with%20Modi%20in%20a%20place%2C%20and%20before%20Vajpayee%20could%20propose%20the%20idea%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20in%20the%20National%20Executive%2C%20Modi%20himself%20offered%20to%20resign.%20As%20planned%2C%20some%20executive%20members%20led%20by%20Advani%20vigorously%20resisted%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20proposal.%20Vajpayee%20sensed%20the%20mood%20and%20ended%20up%20supporting%20Modi%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vyas%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdvani%20was%20a%20darling%20of%20the%20BJP%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20but%20was%20eventually%20pushed%20into%20the%20shadows%20by%20none%20other%20than%20Modi%20after%20he%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%2C%20in%20what%20can%20aptly%20be%20described%20as%20some%20sort%20of%20divine%20justice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%202010%2C%20Advani%20had%20reached%20the%20twilight%20of%20his%20political%20career.%20He%20had%20faced%20the%202009%20loss%2C%20following%20which%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fevergreen%2Flk-advani-interview-ayodhya-yatra-bjp-9142057%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ean%20interview%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20he%20came%20across%20as%20a%20subdued%20leader%20when%20he%20disowned%20even%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20rath%20yatra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20had%20written%20his%20biography%20by%20that%20time%2C%20in%20which%20he%20decried%20the%20demolition%20of%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%20what%20many%20believed%20was%20a%20shrewd%20way%20to%20bypass%20legal%20proceedings%20against%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHad%20I%20known%20how%20it%20would%20end%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20have%20never%20gone%20to%20Ayodhya%2C%20but%20I%E2%80%99d%20still%20have%20gone%20to%20Pakistan%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbook-review-vinay-sitapati-jugalbandi%5C%22%3EBook%20Review%3A%20The%20Yin%20and%20Yang%20in%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Rise%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20yatra%20may%20have%20impressed%20some%2C%20won%20me%20supporters%20and%20made%20my%20opponents%20angrier.%20But%20I%20recall%20that%20as%20a%20time%20of%20major%20education%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Advani%20added%2C%20while%20claiming%20that%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20religious%20tradition%20%E2%80%9Cused%20to%20be%20Sikh%20rituals%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20holy%20book%20at%20his%20home%20being%20the%20Guru%20Granth%20Sahib.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20remarks%20on%20Jinnah%20had%20already%20offended%20a%20large%20section%20of%20his%20friends%20in%20the%20party%2C%20which%20perceived%20the%20comments%20as%20his%20desperation%20to%20be%20seen%20not%20as%20a%20divisive%20leader%20but%20a%20leader%20of%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20journalist%20Kuldeep%20Kumar%20says%20that%20when%20Advani%20called%20Jinnah%20a%20%E2%80%9Csecular%20leader%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20surprising.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20find%20Jinnah%20and%20Advani%20close%20to%20each%20other.%20Jinnah%20proposed%20the%20two-nation%20theory%20along%20religious%20lines.%20He%20wanted%20a%20Muslim%20nation%2C%20while%20Advani%20and%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20wanted%20a%20Hindu%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Erashtra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Both%20draw%20inspiration%20from%20a%20similar%20set%20of%20beliefs%20and%20frame%20nations%20only%20along%20religious%20lines.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENonetheless%2C%20journalists%20who%20have%20closely%20interacted%20with%20Advani%20agree%20that%20he%20was%20an%20extremely%20polite%20and%20warm%20person%2C%20and%20never%20dodged%20questions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAdvani%20would%20answer%20and%20entertain%20even%20his%20critics%2C%20which%20is%20so%20different%20from%20the%20leaders%20in%20the%20BJP%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vyas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20in%20the%20BJP%20articulated%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20ideological%20line%20as%20clearly%20as%20Advani.%20He%20was%20never%20bitter%20in%20his%20talk%2C%20and%20maintained%20a%20healthy%2C%20professional%20relationship%20with%20journalists.%20He%20never%20refused%20to%20answer%20tough%20questions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kumar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20will%20be%20remembered%20for%20the%20direction%20he%20gave%20to%20India%20through%20his%20polarising%20rath%20yatra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAdvani%20played%20the%20most%20prominent%20role%20in%20normalising%20the%20divisions%20that%20you%20see%20in%20India%20today%20in%20all%20its%20crudeness%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumar%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20Advani%20has%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20India%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20with%20Modi%20as%20the%20larger-than-life%20figure%20at%20its%20centre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20in%20conferring%20the%20highest%20honour%20to%20his%20mentor%20whom%20he%20ruthlessly%20sidelined%2C%20Modi%20has%20drawn%20attention%20to%20himself%20once%20again.%20He%20has%20at%20once%20placated%20those%20in%20the%20Hindutva%20camp%20who%20were%20peeved%20at%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20absence%20in%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%E2%80%99s%20consecration%20ceremony%20that%20was%20anyway%20meant%20to%20be%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20solo%20show.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20also%20conveyed%20to%20people%20that%20he%20is%2C%20after%20all%2C%20a%20judicious%20man%20who%20has%20resurrected%20Advani.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20has%20placed%20all%20his%20cards%20on%20the%20table.%20With%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20Advani%20and%20to%20socialist%20icon%20Karpoori%20Thakur%2C%20he%20has%20declared%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi-driven%20Hindutva%20as%20well%20as%20OBC%20politics%20as%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20principal%20play%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20even%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20the%2096-year-old%20Advani%20dodge%20becoming%20a%20mere%20pawn%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20political%20chessboard.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706982206000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03231249%2FRath-yatra-II-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fl-k-advani-from-rath-yatra-to-bharat-ratna%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Why%20even%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20the%2096-year-old%20Advani%20from%20becoming%20a%20mere%20pawn%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20political%20chessboard.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fl-k-advani-from-rath-yatra-to-bharat-ratna%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20strikes%20on%20Iraqi%20town%20of%20al-Qaim%20filmed%22%2C%22c