%20and%20salute%20individual%20contributions%20in%20various%20walks%20of%20life%3B%20but%20the%20highest%20honour%2C%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20invariably%20reflects%20the%20principles%2C%20preferences%2C%20priorities%20and%20sometimes%20the%20prejudices%20of%20the%20regime%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20a%20citizen%20is%20entitled%20to%20some%20bafflement%20as%20to%20the%20following%20question%3A%20what%20possessed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1753660421809066495%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20award%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20And%20which%20Advani%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20honoured%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F04192003%2Fstatecraft.png%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-237577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22233%5C%22%3EThere%20is%2C%20first%2C%20an%20Advani%20till%201990%3B%20a%20one-eyed%20man%20in%20a%20kingdom%20of%20the%20blind%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%2C%20the%20RSS%2FJana%20Sangh%2FBJP%20crowd.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20than%20being%20a%20loyal%2C%20disciplined%20and%20unquestioning%20party%20operative%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20in%20the%20first%20three%20decades%20of%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20public%20life%20to%20arrest%20more%20than%20a%20passing%20attention.%20Throughout%20this%20time%2C%20he%20was%20perennially%20trying%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20his%20smarter%20and%20wiser%20comrade%2C%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20Advani%20would%20not%20even%20deserve%20a%20Padma%20Shri.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20the%20second%20Advani%2C%20who%20in%20a%20game%20of%20one-upmanship%20with%20Vajpayee%2C%20set%20out%20on%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Erath%20yatra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from