C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20he%20not%20only%20failed%20to%20perform%20his%20constitutional%20duty%20when%20Gujarat%20played%20host%20to%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20carnages%20in%20modern%20India%2C%20he%20also%20frustrated%20his%20own%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20stated%20desire%20to%20send%20Narendra%20Modi%20packing%20for%20having%20failed%20to%20perform%20a%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eraj%20dharma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20record%20as%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20was%20to%20collude%20with%20the%20Nagpur%20bosses%20to%20slow%20down%20and%20sabotage%20Prime%20Minister%20Vajpayee.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20was%20thrown%20out%20of%20power%20in%202004%2C%20the%20fourth%20Advani%20was%20in%20the%20market%2C%20with%20prime%20ministerial%20ambitions%20fully%20aroused.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20travelled%20to%20Pakistan%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20soften%20his%20image%20as%20a%20hard-liner%20and%20made%20some%20convoluted%20formulations%20about%20Muhammad%20Ali%20Jinnah.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20became%20a%20victim%20of%20those%20very%20unwholesome%20elements%20in%20and%20outside%20the%20BJP%20whom%20he%20had%20encouraged%20in%20his%20power%20struggle%20against%20Vajpayee.%20He%20had%20the%20ignominy%20of%20being%20asked%20by%20the%20shadowy%20men%20from%20Nagpur%20to%20step%20down%20as%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20president.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-provocateur-in-chief-l-k-advani%5C%22%3EL.K.%20Advani%2C%20the%20Provocateur%20in%20Chief%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fourth%20Advani%20was%20also%20rejected%20by%20the%20electorate%20when%20he%20was%20projected%20as%20the%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20prime%20ministerial%20choice%20against%20Manmohan%20Singh%20in%202009.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20the%20greatest%20political%20defeat%20for%20a%20man%20who%20had%20long-prepared%20himself%20for%20the%20moment%20and%20that%20too%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20political%20rival%20whom%20he%20pooh-poohed%20as%20the%20weakest%20prime%20minister%20India%20had%20known.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Advani%20story%20was%20essentially%20over%20in%202009%20and%20everybody%20except%20him%20recognised%20this.%20The%20hard-cored%20men%20who%20call%20the%20shots%20in%20the%20BJP%20never%20appreciated%20his%20efforts%20to%20refashion%20himself%20as%20a%20moderate%20and%20mild%20leader.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20had%20fallen%20out%20of%20favour%20with%20the%20Nagpur%20commissars%2C%20who%20were%20now%20scouting%20for%20a%20new%20winning%20horse.%20A%20thoroughbred%20was%20already%20straining%20at%20the%20leash%20in%20Gandhinagar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20this%20man%20who%20prided%20himself%20on%20reading%20the%20mood%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekaryakarta%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20in%20his%20own%20party%20failed%20to%20discern%20that%20the%20Modi%20age%20had%20already%20begun%20in%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%2C%20the%20disciple%2C%20was%20no%20longer%20meek%20and%20humble%20and%20had%20no%20qualms%20in%20showing%20Advani%20his%20place%20in%20a%20remote%20corner.%20The%20grand%20old%20man%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20stoically%20pay%20homage%20to%20the%20new%20emperor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F24131929%2FModi-Advani-1024x832.jpg%5C%22%20alt%