%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20king%20is%20assertive%20of%20his%20whims%20and%20fancies.%20So%20be%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fhkhare%5C%22%3EHarish%20Khare%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20former%20editor-in-chief%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Tribune%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706969640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03194156%2FAdvani.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fan-advani-honoured-the-republic-diminished%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20a%20stench%20of%20shabby%20calculations%20in%20L.K.%20Advani%20being%20awarded%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fan-advani-honoured-the-republic-diminished%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It's%20not%20just%20you%20%E2%80%94%20furniture%20is%20garbage%20these%20days.%20Here's%20what%20you%20can%20do%20about%20it.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20large%20couch%20on%20top%20of%20a%20small%20garbage%20can%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aed5bcdcdb354a9859f101%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDumitru%20Ochievschi%2FGetty%2C%20CHIARI_VFX%2FGetty%2C%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20quality%20of%20mass-market%20furniture%20sold%20in%20the%20US%20has%20sharply%20declined.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDesigners%20say%20material%20innovation%2C%20cost%20cutting%2C%20and%20consumer%20behavior%20has%20played%20a%20role.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20between%20shopping%20vintage%2C%20custom%2C%20and%20yes%2C%20the%20big%20box%20stores%2C%20consumers%20have%20options.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMike%20Coleman%20has%20seen%20a%20lot%20in%20his%20five%20years%20selling%20vintage%20furniture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20in%20million-dollar%20mansions%20and%20abandoned%20schools%20%E2%80%94%20and%20found%20the%20same%20exact%20chair%20in%20both%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20things%20that%20stands%20out%20to%20him%20in%20the%20pieces%20he%20sources%20and%20sells%3F%20The%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20still%20constantly%20finding%20pieces%20of%20furniture%20that%20are%2075%20years%20old%2C%20and%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20they%20are%20good%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20Coleman%2C%20who%20owns%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbigmikesvintage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Mike's%20Vintage%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Chicago%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20bet%20all%20the%20money%20in%20my%20pocket%20that%20any%20furniture%20you%20buy%20on%20Amazon%20today%20will%20not%20last%20more%20than%20five%20years%2C%20especially%20if%20it%20says%20'made%20in%20China.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mass%20production%20that%20the%20US%20saw%20in%20the%20mid-20th%20century%20and%20the%20quality%20that%20it%20cranked%20out%20was%20completely%20ridiculous%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BUnimaginable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20happened%20that%20made%20furniture%20experience%20such%20a%20sharp%20decline%20in%20quality%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20variety%20of%20things%20that%20have%20led%20to%20the%20degradation%20of%20quality%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cocoree.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECoCo%20Ree%20Lemery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20furniture%20designer%20and%20visiting%20professor%20at%20Purdue%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInnovation%20in%20materials%2C%20a%20desire%20to%20cut%20costs%2C%20and%20consumer%20preferences%20are%20among%20the%20factors%20that%20have%20led%20here%3A%20where%20customers%20don't%20even%20expect%20pieces%20to%20last%20several%20years%2C%20let%20alone%20decades%20%E2%80%94%20and%20where%20those%20looking%20for%20quality%20are%20increasingly%20turning%20toward%20vintage%20and%20custom%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20decline%20in%20quality%2C%20consumers%20have%20options%2C%20and%20all%20hope%20is%20not%20lost%20for%20people%20looking%20to%20fill%20their%20homes%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20furniture%20their%20kids%20and%20grandkids%20will%20fight%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20shop%20filled%20with%20vintage%20wood%20furniture%20and%20chandeliers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bda0f06fcb546d2d4be2ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReselling%20high-quality%2C%20vintage%20furniture%20is%20a%20growing%20business.%3Cp%3Etaikrixel%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20furniture%20materials%20got%20so%E2%80%A6cheap%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInnovation%20in%20materials%20during%20the%2020th%20century%20disrupted%20the%20furniture%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20material%20landscape%20has%20fundamentally%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Lemery%2C%20who%20has%20designed%20furniture%20for%20brands%20like%20Pottery%20Barn%2C%20Williams%20Sonoma%2C%20and%20Jonathan%20Adler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20mid-1900s%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20furniture%20sold%20in%20the%20US%20was%20made%20of%20solid%20hardwood%20or%20plywood%2C%20sheets%20of%20wood%20that%20are%20glued%20together.%20But%20in%20the%201970s%20and%2080s%2C%20engineered%20wood%20products%20started%20to%20appear%20and%20quickly%20spread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20products%20include%20things%20like%20medium-density%20fiberboard%2C%20oriented%20strand%20board%2C%20and%20particle%20board%2C%20which%20are%20generally%20made%20by%20breaking%20wood%20down%20into%20strips%20or%20fibers%20that%20are%20then%20compressed%20and%20binded%20together%20with%20adhesives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20just%20the%20wood%20material%20that's%20used.%20Even%20screws%20today%20are%20commonly%20made%20of%20brass%2C%20a%20softer%20metal%2C%20rather%20than%20steel.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20every%20component%20that%20then%20combines%20together%20to%20make%20something%20that%20is%20fundamentally%20less%20durable%2C%26quot%3B%20Lemery%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELemery%20said%20companies%20are%20always%20looking%20for%20the%20cheapest%20possible%20materials%3A%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20are%20on%20the%20driver's%20end%20as%20a%20designer%2C%20you're%20trying%20to%20keep%20those%20production%20costs%20as%20low%20as%20possible%20so%20that%20you%20can%20mark%20that%20piece%20of%20furniture%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20lack%20of%20diversity%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20quality.%20With%20hardly%20any%20manufacturing%20in%20the%20US%2C%20many%20furniture%20makers%20end%20up%20outsourcing%20to%20the%20same%20factories%20in%20China%20and%20India.%20Lemery%20said%20when%20she'd%20travel%20to%20the%20factories%20about%20four%20times%20a%20year%20to%20see%20the%20samples%20of%20her%20designs%2C%20she'd%20also%20see%20samples%20from%20several%20other%20brands%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%2C%20they%20were%20all%20being%20produced%20at%20the%20same%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInnovations%20in%20furniture%20have%20not%20been%20all%20bad.%20There's%20a%20certain%20level%20of%20accessibility%20that%20comes%20with%20being%20able%20to%20produce%20large%20pieces%20of%20furniture%20for%20relatively%20low%20prices%2C%20and%20furniture%20that%20can%20be%20shipped%20flat%20and%20built%20at%20home%20also%20has%20its%20benefits.%20A%20lot%20of%20solid%20wood%20furniture%20in%20the%20past%20could%20not%20be%20broken%20down%20into%20pieces%20%E2%80%94%20potentially%20a%20major%20inconvenience%20for%20someone%20who%20moves%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223508%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20factory%20worker%20polishes%20the%20top%20of%20a%20desk%20in%20a%20US%20furniture%20factory%2C%20circa%201950.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bda2fb7a3d271488776a4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222487%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20factory%20worker%20polishes%20the%20top%20of%20a%20desk%20in%20a%20US%20furniture%20factory%2C%20circa%201950.%3Cp%3EJames%20W.%20Welgos%2FArchive%20Photos%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EConsumers%20are%20partly%20to%20blame%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFurniture%20manufacturers%20aren't%20the%20only%20ones%20to%20blame%20for%20this%20shift%20in%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20the%20market%20demand%20is%20for%20hot%20and%20now%20and%20cheap%20and%20that%20production%20follows%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkcad.ferris.edu%2Fprograms%2Ffaculty%2Fdebruyn-gayle.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGayle%20DeBruyn%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20Kendall%20College%20of%20Art%20and%20Design%20of%20Ferris%20State%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20mid-1900s%2C%20buying%20a%20piece%20of%20furniture%20was%20a%20process%20that%20could%20take%20months%2C%20from%20going%20to%20the%20local%20furniture%20place%2C%20picking%20out%20a%20model%20you%20like%2C%20and%20ordering%20one%20for%20your%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20consumers%20now%20are%20accustomed%20to%20the%20idea%20that%20when%20you%20buy%20something%2C%20you%20should%20be%20able%20to%20get%20it%20within%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20also%20expect%20physical%20objects%20to%20be%20relatively%20cheap.%20Lemery%20notes%20that%20you%20can%20buy%20some%20desks%20for%20less%20money%20than%20what%20it%20would%20cost%20to%20buy%20raw%20lumber%20and%20make%20one%20yourself.%20She%20said%20Americans%20tend%20to%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bdemented%26quot%3B%20idea%20of%20what%20things%20actually%20should%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPartly%20in%20response%20to%20that%20consumer%20demand%2C%20fast%20furniture%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20popular.%20Like%20fast%20fashion%2C%20fast%20furniture%20products%20are%20churned%20out%20quickly%20and%20cheaply%2C%20allowing%20consumers%20to%20follow%20trends%20on%20a%20whim%20rather%20than%20invest%20in%20their%20pieces.%20Brands%20like%20Urban%20Outfitters%20and%20Anthropologie%20saw%20huge%20growth%20in%20their%20furniture%20wings%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20Lemery%20said.%20Zara%20and%20Banana%20Republic%20now%20also%20have%20furniture%20and%20home%20goods%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20see%20all%20these%20fast%20fashion%20outlets%20kind%20of%20getting%20into%20furniture%20as%20another%20revenue%20source%2C%20and%20they're%20treating%20it%20the%20same%20way%20as%20they%20do%20fashion%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20rat%20race%20fosters%20the%20perception%20that%20every%20item%20is%20disposable%20or%20replaceable.%20And%20while%20some%20people%20feel%20content%20with%20donating%20furniture%20once%20they%20are%20done%20with%20it%2C%20much%20of%20it%20still%20ultimately%20ends%20up%20in%20a%20landfill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20companies%20are%20exploring%20circular%20design%20for%20furniture%20%E2%80%94%20or%20how%20to%20ensure%20pieces%20do%20not%20end%20up%20in%20the%20landfill%20once%20consumers%20are%20done%20with%20them.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ikea.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fthis-is-ikea%2Fsustainable-everyday%2Fa-circular-ikea-making-the-things-we-love-last-longer-pub9750dd90%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EIkea%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20DeBruyn%20said%20is%20leading%20the%20industry%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20has%20committed%20to%20becoming%20a%20circular%20business%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20says%20it%20wants%20to%20enable%20its%20customers%20to%20buy%2C%20care%20for%2C%20and%20pass%20on%20their%20products%20in%20more%20sustainable%20ways.%20That%20could%20mean%20designing%20furniture%20so%20that%20it%20can%20be%20broken%20down%20and%20the%20materials%20reused%20to%20create%20something%20new%2C%20which%20DeBruyn%20says%20is%20necessary%20for%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Goodwills%20in%20the%20world%20can't%20handle%20all%20that%20furniture%2C%26quot%3B%20DeBruyn%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20scale%20is%20crazy.%20They%20just%20don't%20have%20a%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Discarded%20couches%20and%20trash%20along%20the%20train%20tracks%20along%20Grandee%20Ave%20and%20E%2097th%20St%20in%20Watts%20on%20Thursday%2C%20May%204%2C%202023%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20CA.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bda37c6fcb546d2d4be323%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDiscarded%20couches%20and%20trash%20along%20the%20train%20tracks%20along%20Grandee%20Ave%20and%20E%2097th%20St%20in%20Watts%20on%20Thursday%2C%20May%204%2C%202023%2C%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20CA.%3Cp%3EGary%20Coronado%2FLos%20Angeles%20Times%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20you%20can%20do%20about%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20Mike's%20Vintage%20is%20among%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20businesses%20that%20sell%20curated%20vintage%20goods%20online%2C%20including%20on%20sites%20like%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%20Marketplace.%20Coleman%20says%20his%20customers%20come%20to%20him%20in%20part%20because%20the%20products%20he%20sells%20have%20a%20level%20of%20quality%20that's%20missing%20from%20what%20you%20can%20get%20at%20big%20box%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20about%20where%20you%20look%20for%20quality%20furniture%2C%20but%20also%20about%20rethinking%20the%20decision-making%20process%20before%20purchasing%20a%20piece.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20buying%2C%20DeBruyn%20wants%20to%20%26quot%3Binspire%20people%20to%20ask%20bigger%20questions%20and%20do%20more%20research%20before%20they%20decide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsk%20yourself%20whether%20you%20actually%20like%20the%20piece%20you%20are%20buying%20or%20whether%20you%20are%20just%20trying%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20a%20trend.%20Ask%20what%20materials%20the%20piece%20is%20made%20of%20and%20how%20often%20it%20will%20be%20used.%20Consider%20if%20you%20plan%20to%20move%20soon%20and%20if%20the%20mobility%20of%20the%20item%20is%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20spending%20a%20bit%20more%20money%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20furniture%20will%20be%20worth%20it%2C%20especially%20for%20pieces%20that%20will%20be%20used%20a%20lot%20and%20need%20a%20high%20level%20of%20quality%20and%20functionality%2C%20like%20your%20dining%20room%20table%20or%20primary%20dresser.%20Instead%20of%20only%20looking%20at%20the%20big%20box%20stores%2C%20you%20can%20check%20out%20vintage%20retailers%20or%20even%20custom%20makers%20for%20pieces%20that%20you%20know%20you%20will%20keep%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColeman%2C%20of%20Big%20Mike's%2C%20said%20even%20he%20acknowledges%20that%20in%20today's%20world%2C%20it's%20impossible%20to%20buy%20vintage%20100%25%20of%20the%20time.%20After%20moving%20into%20a%20new%20place%2C%20he%20tried%20for%20weeks%20to%20find%20a%20vintage%20couch%20that%20would%20work.%20When%20he%20couldn't%2C%20he%20turned%20to%20Ikea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBuy%20vintage%20and%20secondhand%20when%20you%20can%20and%20when%20you%20can't%2C%20then%20hit%20the%20big%20box%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20recommends%20getting%20to%20know%20your%20local%20vintage%20dealer%20and%20letting%20them%20know%20what%20you're%20on%20the%20hunt%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20solid%20list%20in%20my%20head%20of%20regular%20customers%20that%20I%20hit%20up%20immediately%20when%20I%20find%20something%20they%20are%20looking%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20When%20he%20can't%20find%20it%2C%20he'll%20refer%20them%20to%20another%20vintage%20seller%20who%20recently%20found%20what%20they're%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20that%20we%20can%20diversify%20our%20purchases%20and%20vote%20with%20our%20wallets%20%E2%80%94%20that%20vintage%20is%20important%2C%20and%20that%20handmade%20is%20important%2C%20and%20that%20there%20is%20a%20beauty%20to%20even%20mass-manufactured%20stuff%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20the%20more%20that%20we%20can%20diversify%20that%2C%20the%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Lemery%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unrealistic%20for%20many%20people%20to%20fill%20their%20homes%20exclusively%20with%20brand-new%2C%20expensive%2C%20high-quality%20furniture.%20She%20hopes%20furniture%20consumption%20can%20simply%20get%20to%20a%20place%20where%20it's%20a%20little%20more%20balanced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20people%20have%2C%20in%20a%20single%20room%2C%20something%20that%20they%20got%20at%20a%20bargain%2C%20something%20that%20they%20invested%20heavily%20in%2C%20and%20something%20that%20they%20found%20vintage%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20the%20perfect%20room%20is%20a%20combination%20of%20all%20the%20elements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffurniture-quality-declined-shop-vintage-custom-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706969281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aed5d1dcdb354a9859f111%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffurniture-quality-declined-shop-vintage-custom-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20quality%20of%20mass-market%20furniture%20in%20the%20US%20has%20plummeted%2C%20but%20designers%20and%20sellers%20say%20consumers%20still%20have%20options.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40insider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffurniture-quality-declined-shop-vintage-custom-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20got%20a%20dangerous%20surgery%20at%2016%20to%20stop%20excessive%20facial%20blushing%2C%20and%20it%20ruined%20my%20life.%20Decades%20later%2C%20I%20can't%20feel%20emotions.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22headshot%20of%20John%20Larsen%20drinking%20coffee%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bbd5a37a3d27148876ac6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20Larsen%20after%20his%20facial-blushing%20surgery.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20John%20Larsen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20he%20was%20a%20kid%2C%20he%20blushed%20a%20lot%20and%20had%20sweaty%20palms%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20your%20average%20teen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAt%2016%2C%20he%20got%20an%20endoscopic%20thoracic%20sympathectomy%20to%20correct%20his%20excessive%20facial%20blushing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe's%20now%2040%20and%20still%20suffering%20the%20side%20effects%20from%20the%20surgery%3B%20he%20can't%20feel%20emotions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20John%20Larsen.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-parents-marriage-relationship-fear-commitment-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrowing%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20outgoing%20and%20enjoyed%20being%20in%20front%20of%20people%2C%20but%20as%20I%20reached%20adolescence%2C%20I%20became%20increasingly%20aware%20of%20a%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20turn%20beet-red%20in%20embarrassing%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20teenager%2C%20that%20was%20problematic%20and%20limiting.%20I%20couldn't%20do%20the%20things%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%3A%20feel%20comfortable%20approaching%20a%20girl%2C%20speak%20in%20front%20of%20the%20class%2C%20do%20drama.%20I'd%20go%20crimson%20every%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20had%20excessively%20sweaty%20palms.%20Together%2C%20these%20things%20made%20me%20feel%20even%20more%20self-conscious%20than%20your%20usual%20teen.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fwhat-is-depression%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efelt%20depressed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20other%20kids%20at%20school%20would%20notice%20and%20comment%3A%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20my%20God%2C%20you're%20so%20red.%20What's%20wrong%20with%20you%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20tried%20beta%20blockers%20first%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20my%20doctor%20prescribed%20beta%20blockers.%20They%20slow%20your%20heart%20rate%20and%20can%20reduce%20facial%20redness.%20They%20worked%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20I%20wasn't%20keen%20on%20taking%20a%20pill%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%20that%20could%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fside-effects-of-semaglutide-wegoy-ozempicweight-loss-drug-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eside%20effects%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20I%20first%20read%20about%20endoscopic%20thoracic%20sympathectomies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20surgery%20is%20most%20often%20sought%20to%20mitigate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fhow-to-stop-sweating%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexcessive%20sweating%3C%2Fa%3E%20(usually%20of%20the%20palms)%2C%20but%20sometimes%20it's%20used%20for%20facial%20blushing.%20I%20thought%20it'd%20be%20great%20to%20deal%20with%20my%20uncomfortably%20sweaty%20palms.%20But%20my%20primary%20reason%20was%20the%20facial%20flushing.%20I%20just%20wanted%20it%20to%20stop%20holding%20me%20back.%20I%20persuaded%20my%20mom%20to%20go%20with%20me%20for%20a%20consultation.%20I%20was%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20told%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-companies-reimagining-doctors-visits-with-virtual-in-person-care-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprimary-care%20doctor%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20ETS%20surgery%2C%20and%20they%20looked%20into%20it%20for%20me.%20They%20referred%20me%20to%20a%20dermatologist%20who%20assessed%20the%20issues%20arising%20from%20my%20blushing%20and%20sweating.%20I%20was%20then%20referred%20to%20a%20specialist%20surgeon%20who%20dealt%20specifically%20in%20the%20thoracic%20region%20of%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMom%20was%20cautious%20and%20a%20little%20worried.%20But%20from%20what%20we%20were%20reading%2C%20the%20procedure%20seemed%20safe.%20No%20mother%20wants%20to%20see%20her%20child%20suffer.%20She%20was%20supportive%20based%20on%20the%20information%20we%20learned%20from%20the%20doctor%20and%20our%20reading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20surgeon%20glossed%20over%20the%20side%20effects%20like%20they%20were%20nothing%20to%20worry%20about.%20He%20briefly%20mentioned%20I%20might%20get%20some%20excessive%20sweating%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20my%20body.%20That%20was%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20I%20got%20the%20surgery%2C%20I%20was%2016.%20It%20involves%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedlineplus.gov%2Fency%2Farticle%2F007291.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edeflating%20the%20lungs%20one%20at%20a%20time%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20then%20destroying%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20sympathetic%20nerve%20trunk%20in%20the%20thoracic%20region%2C%20which%20disrupts%20neural%20messages%20that%20give%20the%20brain%20signals%20about%20emotional%20reactions%2C%20environmental%20changes%20such%20as%20temperature%2C%20and%20triggers%20including%20fight%20or%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20side%20effects%20have%20lasted%20decades%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20surgery%20took%20less%20than%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20it%20has%20changed%20my%20whole%20life.%20I'm%2040%20now%20and%20still%20experiencing%20weird%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eside%20effects%20%E2%80%94%20none%20of%20which%20were%20disclosed%20beforehand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fairness%2C%20my%20hands%20are%20now%20mostly%20dry.%20And%20the%20facial%20flushing%20initially%20improved%2C%20though%20it%20wasn't%20completely%20resolved.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20devastated%20about%20that.%20I'd%20wanted%20to%20get%20my%20life%20back.%20It'd%20come%20to%20be%20the%20least%20of%20my%20worries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lifelong%20side%20effects%20of%20ETS%20surgery%20have%20been%20brutal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20that%2C%20for%20some%2C%20cutting%20the%20sympathetic%20nerve%20reduces%20responses%20to%20strong%20emotions%2C%20such%20as%20fear%20or%20laughter.%20I'm%20now%20robotic%20in%20my%20emotional%20states.%20There's%20an%20ever-present%20fog%3B%20I%20feel%20disassociated.%20ETS%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforum.effectivealtruism.org%2Fposts%2F6o7CuxJGcnckTkg49%2Fsympathectomies-the-new-lobotomy-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecompared%20to%20a%20modern-day%20lobotomy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20some%20who've%20suffered%20similar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmL50n4-xskc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eside%20effects%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20robbed%20of%20my%20adult%20emotions.%20But%20I%20know%20I'm%20missing%20something.%20It's%20often%20pointed%20out%20by%20those%20around%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20barbaric%20side%20effects%2C%20such%20as%20thermal%20dysregulation.%20I%20have%20varying%20body%20temperatures%20occurring%20at%20once.%20It's%20a%20never-ending%20battle.%20There%20are%20bed%20stains%20from%20how%20much%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fproducts-that-prevent-night-sweats%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esweat%20at%20night%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20on%20my%20neck%2C%20back%2C%20and%20chest.%20This%20happens%20even