%20while%20he%20respects%20the%20humble%20beginnings%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20he%20has%20lost%20touch%20with%20the%20common%20people%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20sad%20part%20is%20that%20he%20has%20taken%20his%20chair%20to%20such%20a%20height%20that%20he%20cannot%20listen%20to%20the%20problems%20faced%20by%20the%20people.%20He%20cannot%20see%20the%20tears%20of%20the%20unemployed%20youth.%20He%20has%20reached%20such%20a%20height%20that%20he%20cannot%20see%20educated%20unemployed%20graduates.%20In%20the%20search%20for%20jobs%2C%20our%20youth%20are%20leaving%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gogoi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20few%20days%20back%20a%20movie%20called%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Dunki%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20released.%20Dunki%20is%20not%20merely%20a%20movie%2C%20it%20is%20the%20reality%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gogoi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20the%20government%20itself%20had%20admitted%20that%20illegal%20immigration%20by%20Indian%20immigrants%20have%20increased.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202022-23%2C%2090%2C000%20people%20tried%20to%20enter%20the%20US%20illegally%2C%20sometimes%20from%20Canada%2C%20sometimes%20from%20Mexico.%20They%20are%20forced%20to%20go%20to%20the%20UAE%2C%20Canada%20and%20America%2C%20leaving%20their%20families%20and%20homes%20behind%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gogoi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20maharaja%20is%20sitting%20on%20such%20a%20high%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esinghasan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bchair%5D%20that%20he%20cannot%20see%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706967944000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03184509%2FGaurav-Gogoi.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-mp-gaurav-gogoi-interrup