0459%2Fimage-1809.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Thousands%20of%20protesters%20on%20Saturday%20(February%203)%20rallied%20in%20the%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20districts%20of%20Ladakh%20in%20response%20to%20a%20shutdown%20call%20against%20the%20constitutional%20changes%20brought%20about%20by%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complete%20shutdown%20in%20the%20region%20was%20called%20by%20the%20Leh%20Apex%20Body%20(LAB)%20and%20Kargil%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(KDA)%2C%20two%20influential%20groups%20who%20are%20spearheading%20an%20agitation%20to%20demand%20special%20rights%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20after%20the%20region%20was%20separated%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20groups%20have%20been%20demanding%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20for%20Ladakh%2C%20which%20was%20downgraded%20into%20a%20Union%20territory%20without%20a%20legislature%20in%202019.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20seek%20tribal%20status%20for%20Ladakh%2C%20with%20its%20inclusion%20in%20the%20constitution%E2%80%99s%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20job%20reservation%20for%20locals%20and%20a%20parliamentary%20seat%20each%20for%20the%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%20received%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20shutdown%20was%20observed%20in%20both%20the%20districts%2C%20with%20businesses%20suspending%20their%20daily%20activities%2C%20even%20in%20the%20remote%20Zanskar%20and%20Nubra%20Valley%20regions%2C%20while%20public%20transport%20remained%20largely%20off-roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FpV0QWtXZ20g%3Fsi%3Dzvz-mRiSaWAQ0idd%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20intense%20cold%2C%20the%20protesters%2C%20including%20peop