2F2016%2F07%2Fgavel.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bombay%20high%20court%20on%20Tuesday%20(January%2030)%20said%20that%20breaching%20a%20marriage%20promise%20due%20to%20parental%20opposition%20does%20not%20amount%20to%20rape.%20The%20Nagpur%20bench%20of%20the%20court%20made%20these%20comments%20while%20discharging%20a%20man%20from%20a%20rape%20case%20where%20he%20was%20accused%20of%20fraudulently%20obtaining%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20there%20was%20a%20difference%20between%20breaching%20a%20promise%20and%20not%20fulfilling%20a%20false%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%20in%20the%20case%20said%20that%20she%20and%20the%20accused%20became%20physically%20involved%20after%20he%20promised%20to%20her%20that%20they%20would%20get%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20accused%20engaged%20himself%20to%20another%20woman%2C%20following%20which%20the%20complainant%20approached%20the%20police%20in%202019%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbombayhighcourt.nic.in%2Fgeneratepdf.php%3Fbhcpar%3DcGF0aD0uL3dyaXRlcmVhZGRhdGEvZGF0YS9uYWdqdWRnZW1lbnRzLzIwMjQvJmZuYW1lPTIzMzMwMDAwMDQ1MjAyM18xMi5wZGYmc21mbGFnPU4mcmp1ZGRhdGU9JnVwbG9hZGR0PTAxLzAyLzIwMjQmJnNwYXNzcGhyYXNlPTAxMDIyNDE4MDQyNCZuY2l0YXRpb249MjAyNDpCSEMtTkFHOjEyNzMmc21jaXRhdGlvbj0mZGlnY2VydGZsZz1ZJmludGVyZmFjZT1O%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbombayhighcourt.nic.in%2Fgeneratepdf.php%3Fbhcpar%3DcGF0aD0uL3dyaXRlcmVhZGRhdGEvZGF0YS9uYWdqdWRnZW1lbnRzLzIwMjQvJmZuYW1lPTIzMzMwMDAwMDQ1MjAyM18xMi5wZGYmc21mbGFnPU4mcmp1ZGRhdGU9JnVwbG9hZGR0PTAxLzAyLzIwMjQmJnNwYXNzcGhyYXNlPTAxMDIyNDE4MDQyNCZuY2l0YXRpb249MjAyNDpCSEMtTkFHOjEyNzMmc21jaXRhdGlvbj0mZGlnY2VydGZsZz1ZJmludGVyZmFjZT1O%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Ethe%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20cited%20her%20complaint%20and%20the%20subsequent%20FIR%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20cited%20them%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20complainant%20met%20the%20accused%E2%80%99s%20parents%20after%20learning%20of%20his%20engagement%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Chis%20father%20refused%20to%20agree%20for%20the%20marriage%20of%20the%20applicant%20%5Bthe%20accused%5D%20with%20the%20victim%20%5Bthe%20complainant%5D%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20ruled%2C%20citing%20evidence%2C%20that%20the%20accused%E2%80%99s%20withdrawal%20from%20his%20commitment%20to%20marriage%20due%20to%20his%20parents%E2%80%99%20disagreement%20with%20their%20union%20does%20not%20warrant%20charging%20him%20with%20the%20offence%20punishable%20under%20Section%20375%20(rape)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20had%20approached%20the%20high%20court%20for%20relief%20after%20a%20local%20sessions%20court%20rejected%20his%20application%20to%20be%20discharged%20from%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecutor%20argued%20that%20as%20per%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20accused%20obtained%20the%20complainant%E2%80%99s%20consent%20%E2%80%9Cunder%20false%20promise%20of%20marriage%20and%20since%20inception%2C%20the%20applicant%20%5Bthe%20accused%5D%20had%20no%20intention%20to%20marry%20the%20victim%20%5Bthe%20complainant%5D%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20since%20the%20accused%20obtained%20the%20complainant%E2%80%99s%20consent%20on%20false%20premises%2C%20Section%20375%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20which%20deals%20with%20rape%2C%20would%20apply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20accused%20argued%20that%20he%20had%20offered%20to%20marry%20the%20complainant%20but%20that%20she%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20interested%20at%20all%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20bench%20comprising%20Justice%20M.W.%20Chandwani%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20also%20appears%20from%20the%20WhatsApp%20chats%20between%20the%20applicant%20and%20the%20victim%20that%2C%20initially%20the%20applicant%20was%20ready%20to%20marry%20the%20victim%2C%20but%20it%20is%20the%20victim%2C%20who%20denied%20and%20informed%20the%20applicant%20that%20she%20will%20marry%20another%20boy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20only%20when%20the%20applicant%20got%20engaged%20with%20another%20girl%2C%20the%20victim%20lodged%20the%20complaint.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20accused%E2%80%99s%20withdrawal%20from%20his%20commitment%2C%20Justice%20Chandwani%20also%20cited%20two%20Supreme%20Court%20judgements%20which%20had%20said%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdistinction%20between%20the%20mere%20breach%20of%20a%20promise%20and%20not%20fulfilling%20a%20false%20promise%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20quashed%20the%20session%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20rejecting%20the%20accused%E2%80%99s%20discharge%20application%20and%20proceeded%20to%20discharge%20him%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706957803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Fgavel.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbreach-of-promise-different-not-fulfilling-false-promise-bombay-hc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20complainant%20in%20the%20case%20said%20the%20accused%20obtained%20her%20consent%20on%20the%20false%20promise%20of%20marriage%2C%20but%20the%20court%20decided%20that%20the%20accused%20intended%20to%20keep%20his%20promise%20but%20ultimately%20was%20not%20able%20to.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbreach-of-promise-different-not-fulfilling-false-promise-bombay-hc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ashoke%20Pandit%3A%20A%20case%20should%20be%20filed%20against%20Poonam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706957608000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107384800%2Cimgsize-65524.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood