Nigerian%20national%20Eze%20Uchenna%20James%20(49)%2C%20Alitumo%20Ifedi%20Shedrack%20(28)%2C%20Eze%20Ibe%20Emeka%20Chibuzo%20alias%20Iko%20(56)%20and%20Kenyan%20national%20Ivo%20Osita%20alias%20Usta%20alias%20Osey%20(44)%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20Eze%2C%20Alitumo%20and%20Ivo%20were%20previously%20arrested%20and%20convicted%20in%20drug%20trafficking%20cases%20and%20were%20out%20on%20conditional%20bail%2C%20according%20to%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Dwarka)%20Ankit%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drug%20bust%20was%20part%20of%20an%20ongoing%20operation%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20against%20the%20suppliers%20of%20narcotics%20substances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2027%2C%202023%2C%20a%20team%20of%20the%20Anti-Narcotics%20Cell%20of%20Dwarka%20district%20got%20a%20secret%20tip-off%20about%20a%20Nigerian%20national%20being%20involved%20in%20a%20drug%20syndicate.%20The%20team%20conducted%20a%20raid%20and%20caught%20Eze%20from%20Uttam%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Eze's%20arrest%2C%20his%20associate%20Alitumo%20was%20caught%20from%20the%20same%20area%20of%20Uttam%20Nagar%20on%20January%2011%20and%20about%20100%20grams%20of%20methamphetamine%20drug%20was%20recovered%20from%20his%20possession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20Alitumo%20along%20with%20Ibe%20and%20Ivo%20used%20to%20manufacture%20fine-quality%20methamphetamine%20drug%20in%20the%20Greater%20Noida-based%20lab%2C%20a%20raid%20was%20conducted%20and%20all%20of%20them%20were%20caught%20on%20January%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20the%20accused%20used%20to%20distribute%20the%20drugs%20to%20their%20potential%20customers%20in%20Delhi%20and%20nearby%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706774580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ftuagh2dg_methamphetamine-drug-bust_625x300_01_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fnoida-news%2Fmethamp