A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F01%2F31%2Fnews%2Fchinese-man-mistress-executed-for-throwing-his-two-young-kids-out-apartment-window-so-they-could-start-a-new-family-together-report%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20report%20that%20Zhang%20started%20an%20affair%20with%20Ye%20without%20telling%20her%20that%20he%20was%20married%20and%20had%20two%20children.%20He%20divorced%20his%20then-wife%20Chen%20Meilin%20in%20February%202020%2C%20but%20was%20forced%20by%20Ye%20to%20kill%20his%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideos%20surfaced%20on%20Chinese%20social%20media%20that%20showed%20Zhang%20grief-stricken%20at%20what%20he%20had%20just%20done.%20He%20was%20also%20seen%20banging%20his%20head%20on%20the%20wall%20and%20sobbing%20uncontrollably%2C%20according%20to%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZhang%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20was%20sleeping%20when%20the%20children%20%26quot%3Bfell%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20he%20woke%20up%20to%20people%20shouting%20downstairs.%20The%20children's%20mother%20said%20she%20was%20shocked%20to%20hear%20what%20happened%20with%20the%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20moment%20I%20heard%20my%20kids%20were%20actually%20thrown%20out%20of%20the%2015th%20floor%20by%20their%20father%20and%20the%20mistress%2C%20I%20couldn't%20find%20any%20words%20to%20describe%20my%20feelings%2C%26quot%3B%20Chen%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20imagine%20what%20my%20kids%20had%20experienced%20from%20the%2015th%20floor%20to%20the%20ground.%20Were%20they%20desperate%3F%20Were%20they%20afraid%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZhang%20and%20Ye's%20crime%20sent%20shock%20waves%20across%20China%20for%20its%20cold-blooded%20premeditation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20executions%20quickly%20rose%20to%20the%20top%20of%20a%20list%20of%20trending%20topics%20on%20Chinese%20social%20media%20site%20Weib