0In%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20RWA%20president%20said%20the%20association%20was%20approached%20by%20residents%20of%20the%20colony%20over%20her%20social%20media%20%26quot%3Bstand%2Frant%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20consecration%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RWA%20accused%20Suranya%20of%20%26quot%3Bhate%20speech%26quot%3B%20and%20requested%20her%20to%20follow%20the%20norms%20of%20a%20good%20citizen.%20It%20claimed%20the%20colony%20was%20inhabited%20by%20residents%20who%20came%20to%20India%20from%20Pakistan%20after%20partition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20erupted%20when%20the%2049-year-old%2C%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%20on%20January%2020%2C%20had%20claimed%20that%20she%20was%20fasting%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20'pran%20pratishtha'%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%20She%20said%20it%20was%20an%20expression%20of%20love%20and%20sorrow%20for%20fellow%20Muslim%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20Ms%20Aiyar%20said%20through%20social%20media%20was%20unbecoming%20of%20an%20educated%20person%2C%20who%20should%20have%20understood%20that%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20was%20being%20built%20after%20500%20years%20and%20that%20too%20after%205-0%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RWA%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20RWA%20notice%2C%20she%20said%20the%20reasons%20for%20her%20disagreement%20were%20expressed%20by%20her%20in%20a%20previous%20speech%20(video)%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20made%20a%20spiritual%20presentation%20of%20my%20own%20pain%20about%20this%20by%20fasting%20peacefully%20in%20my%20home%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20matters%20is%20that%20whatever%20point%20of%20view%20we%20put%20forward%2C%20whether%20people%20can%20see%20some%20sense%20in%20it.%20And%20if%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20process%2C%20in%20India%2C%20we%20can%20even%20just%20find%20a%20more%20civilised%2C%20a%20more%20thinking%20and%20a%20more%20sincere%20way%20of%20talking%20and%20feeling%20about%20these%20things%2C%20then%20we%20would%20have%20achieved%20something%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20stressing%20that%20she%20studied%20abroad%20and%20was%20involved%20with%20activism%20with%20people%20of%20all%20political%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20development%2C%20the%20BJP%20said%20the%20action%20of%20the%20RWA%20should%20serve%20as%20a%20message%20to%20everyone%20who%20believes%20abusing%20Hindu%20beliefs%20is%20%26quot%3Bpar%20for%20the%20course%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RWA%20has%20%26quot%3Basked%20Congress%20leader%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20and%20his%20daughter%20to%20apologise%20for%20defiling%20the%20Pran%20Pratistha%20ceremony%20at%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20and%20leave%20the%20residential%20colony%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20IT%20department%20head%20Amit%20Malviya%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20is%20yet%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'pran%20pratishtha'%20or%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20-%20headlined%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20-%20was%20held%20at%20the%20newly%20built%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706767440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fe0l77j5o_suranya-aiyar-facebook_625x300_01_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmani-shankar-aiyars-daughter-on-move-out-notice-by-delhi-colony-over-ram-temple-i-dont-live-there-4971691%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senior%20Congress%20leader%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar's%20daughter%20Suranya%20Aiyar%2C%20who%20was%20asked%20to%20vacate%20%26quot%3Btheir%26quot%3B%20house%20in%20south-east%20Delhi%20over%20her%20Ram%20Temple%20post%2C%20has%20said%20that%20she%20doesn't%20even%20live%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmani-shankar-aiyars-daughter-on-move-out-notice-by-