barfi%20mithais%20are%20served%20in%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Harshit%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20thus%20grew%20the%20fame%20of%20Janta%20Dairy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers%20hardly%20remember%20seeing%20their%20father%20at%20home.%20Harshit%20goes%20on%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20see%2C%20my%20father%20has%20gone%20to%20the%20shop%20every%20single%20day%2C%20ever%20since%20he%20took%20over%20in%20Class%2012.%20He%20has%20never%20missed%20work.%20It%E2%80%99s%20home%2C%20shop%2C%20and%20back%20home%20for%20dinner.%20Even%20on%20Sundays%2C%20the%20routine%20continues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20one%20day%2C%20the%20routine%20stopped.%20The%20COVID%20pandemic%20had%20extended%20its%20reach%20to%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReimagining%20old-school%20classics%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20disheartening%20for%20the%20boys%20to%20watch%20their%20father%2C%20who%20loved%20the%20dairy%2C%20now%20sit%20at%20home.%20Business%20was%20at%20an%20all-time%20low.%20And%20somewhere%2C%20Harshit%20felt%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331406%2Fwrestler-parmanand-jain-started-mahaveer-rabri-bhandar-became-iconic-eatery-of-jaipur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20legacy%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20going%20to%20falter%20unless%20they%20stepped%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPistabarfi%20was%20born%20out%20of%20a%20quest%20to%20save%20a%20heirloom%20business.%20Though%20testing%20new%20waters%2C%20the%20brothers%20say%20there%20was%20absolutely%20no%20friction.%20Tanay%20brought%20his%20expertise%20in%20dealing%20with%20the%20logistics%2C%20while%20Harshit%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20creative%20aspect%20of%20the%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20was%20for%20the%20family%20to%20continue%20selling%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E%20through%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A