0brother-in-law%20was%20murdered%20following%20a%20business%20rivalry.%20A%20shocking%20development%2C%20it%20left%20his%20family%20dealing%20with%20a%20crisis.%20But%2C%20amid%20this%20crisis%2C%20he%20saw%20something%20that%20would%20leave%20an%20indelible%20impression.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20many%20influential%20people%20with%20notorious%20criminal%20backgrounds%20involved%20in%20this%20murder%20case.%20Fortunately%2C%20we%20had%20a%20very%20good%20police%20officer%20who%20fairly%20investigated%20the%20case.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20best%20of%20what%20a%20police%20officer%20can%20do%20and%20the%20impact%20they%20can%20have%20on%20our%20society.%20As%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20law%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20help%20our%20family%2C%20manage%20other%20professionals%20engaged%20in%20this%20investigation%2C%20and%20nab%20the%20culprits%20as%20well.%20Instead%20of%20becoming%20a%20doctor%2C%20I%20felt%20I%20could%20be%20more%20useful%20to%20society%20as%20a%20police%20officer%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Dr%20Naik.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Dr%20Naik%20struggles%20to%20recall%20the%20name%20of%20the%20officer%20who%20solved%20his%20brother-in-law%E2%80%99s%20murder%20more%20than%2030%20years%20after%20it%20happened%2C%20he%20cannot%20forget%20the%20impression%20the%20episode%20left%20behind.%20Of%20course%2C%20with%20other%20family%20members%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20service%20motivating%20him%20to%20make%20that%20transition%20to%20a%20career%20in%20the%20IPS%2C%20this%20memory%20remained%20seared%20in%20his%20consciousness.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20MBBS%20in%201996%2C%20he%20served%20as%20a%20doctor%20for%20three%20years%20until%201999%20when%20he%20decided%20that%20he%20needed%20a%20complete%20shift%20away%20from%20a%20career%20in%20medicine.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20my%20third%20year%20onwards%2C%20I%20began%20preparing%20for%20the%20UPSC%20exam.%20I%20was%20simultaneously%20studying%20for%20my%20MBBS%20and%20preparing%20for%20the%20Union%20Civil%20Services%20exam.%20Following%20my%20MBBS%2C%20I%20worked%20at%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Visakhapatnam%20for%20a%20short%20while%20before%20leaving%20for%20Hyderabad%20to%20join%20UPSC%20coaching%20classes.%20To%20support%20myself%20financially%2C%20however%2C%20I%20even%20worked%20at%20the%20Apollo%20Hospital%20in%20Jubilee%20Hills%20as%20an%20emergency%20physician%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20decision%20to%20quit%20medicine%20and%20prepare%20%5Bfull-time%5D%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F308203%2Fhow-to-prepare-for-upsc-cse-for-working-professionals-ias-divya-mittal-shares-tips-on-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%20exam%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20met%20by%20vehement%20opposition%20in%20the%20family.%20They%20wanted%20me%20to%20continue%20as%20a%20doctor%20and%20earn%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20attempt%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20reached%20the%20interview%20stage%20but%20missed%20out.%20But%20helping%20him%20along%20the%20way%20were%20a%20few%20friends%20he%20had%20known%20since%20primary%20school.%20They%20were%20also%20preparing%20for%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20supported%20me%20a%20lot.%20They%20could%20not%20get%20through%20but%20they%20were%20happy%20that%20I%20did%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20faith%20in%20Dr%20Naik%20would%20eventually%20pay%20off%20as%20he%20cleared%20the%20interview%20stage%20in%20his%20next%20attempt.%20He%20joined%20the%20IPS%20in%202002%20as%20part%20of%20the%20DANIPS%20(Delhi%2C%20Andaman%20%26amp%3B%20Nicobar%20Islands%2C%20Lakshadweep%2C%20Dadra%2C%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli%20and%20Daman%20and%20Diu%20Police%20Service)%20cadre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20becoming%20an%20IPS%20officer%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20has%20gone%20on%20to%20achieve%20a%20great%20deal.%20From%20receiving%20a%20special%20commendation%20from%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20for%20organising%20relief%20operations%20after%20Cyclone%20HUD%20HUD%20in%202014%20to%20investigating%20and%20extraditing%20Sanjeev%20Chawla%2C%20the%20bookmaker%20famously%20involved%20with%20the%20deceased%20cricket%20player%20Hansie%20Cronje%2C%20in%20fixing%20matches%20between%20India%20and%20South%20Africa%20in%202000%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20has%20many%20achievements%20to%20his%20name.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20notable%20achievements%20include%20initiating%20the%20modernisation%20process%20of%20the%20Lakshadweep%20Police%20during%20his%20first%20official%20posting%20and%20investigating%20and%20solving%20the%202008%20bomb%20blasts%20in%20the%20M-Block%20Market%20of%20Greater%20Kailash%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20In%202018%2C%20he%20also%20solved%20the%20paper%20leak%20case%20of%20the%20CBSE%20Class%2012%20economics%20and%20Class%2010%20mathematics%20examinations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20won%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Police%20Medal%20for%20Gallantry%20in%20January%202021%20for%20conducting%20a%20daring%20rescue%20operation%20of%20a%20kidnapped%205-year-old%20boy%20in%20Sahibabad%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(UP).%20During%20his%20career%2C%20he%20has%20investigated%20a%20plethora%20of%20cases%20but%20this%20one%20stands%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERam%20Gopal%20Naik%2C%20DCP%20Crime%20Branch%3A%20Delhi%20Police%20Crime%20Branch%20with%20help%20of%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20and%20Home%20Affairs%20was%20trying%20to%20get%20him%20(Sanjeev%20Chawla).In%202013%2C%20extradition%20process%20started.%20We%20have%20got%2012-days%20custody.We%20have%20not%20yet%20questioned%20him%2Cprocess%20will%20start%20now.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FI4yOF3swVS%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FI4yOF3swVS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1227948459468025856%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2013%2C%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERescuing%20a%20child%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2025%20January%202018%2C%20as%20preparations%20for%20that%20year%E2%80%99s%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%20were%20in%20full%20force%2C%20a%20five-year-old%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20businessman%20in%20Northeast%20Delhi%20was%20kidnapped.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fdelhi-police-crack-daring-kidnapping-12-day-hunt-ends-in-gunfire-and-a-rescued-child-5054121%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%20kidnapping%2C%20the%20accused%20conducted%20a%20recce%20of%20the%20area%20for%20over%20a%20month%20and%20decided%20to%20target%20the%20school%20bus.%20They%20made%20three%20failed%20attempts%20on%20January%2021%2C%2022%20and%2023.%E2%80%9D%20Speaking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20the%20then%20JCP%20(Crime%20Branch)%20Alok%20Kumar%20identified%20the%20accused%20as%20Nitin%20Sharma%2C%20Ravi%20Kumar%2C%20and%20Pankaj%20alias%20Singh%20Saheb.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20three%20suspects%20had%20hatched%20a%20plan%20to%20kidnap%20the%20child%20after%20%E2%80%9CSunny%20Gupta%2C%20father%20of%20the%20child%2C%20recently%20finalised%20a%20real%20estate%20deal%20of%20Rs%2060%20lakh.%20The%20details%20of%20the%20deal%20were%20common%20knowledge%20of%20everyone%20who%20stayed%20in%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20locality%20GTB%20Enclave.%20Nitin%20thought%20he%20could%20earn%20a%20good%20ransom%20if%20he%20kidnapped%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20son.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20morning%20of%2025%20January%2C%20when%20the%20school%20van%20was%20approaching%20the%20school%2C%20the%20kidnappers%20intercepted%20it%20and%20snatched%20the%20boy%20for%20ransom.%20The%20kidnappers%20shot%20the%20driver%20in%20the%20leg%20and%20took%20the%20boy%20to%20a%20two-bedroom%20flat%20in%20Sahibabad%E2%80%99s%20Shalimar%20City%20apartments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20working%20as%20DCP%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20Crime%20Branch.%20Initially%2C%20the%20case%20was%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20local%20police.%20For%20a%20week%2C%20the%20local%20police%20could%20not%20get%20any%20leads.%20Given%20that%20the%20incident%20happened%20a%20day%20before%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247811%2Frepublic-day-president-address-to-the-nation-speech-constitution-ram-nath-kovind-abdul-kalam-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERepublic%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20Commissioner%20to%20solve%20this%20case%20and%20rescue%20the%20boy.%20My%20commissioner%20took%20a%20call%20that%20the%20case%20should%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20Crime%20Branch%20and%20I%20was%20selected%20to%20handle%20this%20sensitive%20investigation%20given%20that%20a%20boy%E2%80%99s%20life%20was%20at%20stake%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Dr%20Naik%E2%80%99s%20team%20took%20over%20the%20case%2C%20they%20deployed%20their%20sources%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20brought%20on%20officers%20with%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20knowledge%20of%20criminal%20networks%20in%20Northeast%20Delhi%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20our%20officers%20eventually%20got%20a%20lead%20that%20three%20persons%20were%20missing%20in%20the%20area%20where%20the%20boy%20was%20picked%20up%20and%20that%20they%20may%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20case.%20We%20also%20went%20through%20their%20criminal%20records%20and%20posited%20that%20they%20could%20be%20involved.%20Meanwhile%2C%20we%20also%20kept%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20father%20of%20the%20boy%20who%20was%20receiving%20calls%20for%20a%20ransom.%20Besides%20these%20calls%2C%20he%20was%20also%20receiving%20videos%20%5Bon%20WhatsApp%5D%20of%20the%20kidnappers%20claiming%20that%20they%20have%20his%20son%20and%20voice%20recordings%20too%20where%20he%20could%20hear%20his%20son%20pleading%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98Papa%2C%20I%20love%20you%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20dealing%20with%20kidnappers%2C%20they%20also%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20terrified%20father.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20probably%20felt%20that%20cooperating%20with%20the%20police%20would%20put%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20life%20at%20risk.%20Thus%2C%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20being%20very%20cooperative.%20The%20kidnappers%20had%20demanded%20Rs%2060%20lakh%20as%20ransom%20and%20we%20asked%20him%20to%20negotiate%20to%20buy%20some%20time%20and%20trace%20these%20calls.%20But%20we%20believe%20he%20was%20actively%20hiding%20things%20from%20us.%20We%20discovered%20that%20he%20was%20even%20arranging%20the%20money%20to%20pay%20off%20the%20kidnappers%20so%20that%20his%20child%20could%20come%20back%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20recalls%20that%20his%20team%20%E2%80%9Cengaged%20in%20some%20ethical%20hacking%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20father%E2%80%99s%20phone%20so%20that%20they%20could%20have%20first-hand%20information%20about%20what%20was%20being%20discussed.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20kidnappers%20set%20a%20date%20and%20location%20for%20the%20exchange.%20After%20this%20conversation%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20took%20the%20father%20into%20confidence%20and%20assured%20him%20that%20they%20would%20rescue%20his%20child.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E