ecutive%20comes%20and%20picks%20up%20their%20waste.%20The%20consumer%20can%20go%20to%20the%20application%20and%20collect%20their%20reward%20points.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20application%20has%20a%20variety%20of%20products%20that%20consumers%20can%20buy.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20usually%20have%20household%20stuff%20and%20groceries%20which%20the%20consumers%20can%20buy%20for%20free.%20We%20deliver%20them%20to%20their%20homes%20within%2072%20hours%20without%20a%20delivery%20charge.%20So%20basically%2C%20you%20get%20something%20for%20nothing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20limit%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311633%2Fruhani-verma-built-indias-first-carbon-negative-recyclable-public-toilet-amritsar-airport%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eamount%20of%20waste%20%3C%2Fa%3Eyou%20need%20to%20be%20picked%20up%2C%20and%20the%20rewards%20are%20based%20on%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20waste%20collected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20waste%20is%20collected%2C%20Abhishek%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20comes%20to%20our%20storage%20units%20where%20it%20is%20segregated%20again.%20The%20dry%20waste%20collected%20is%20segregated%20into%2040%20categories%20including%20paper%2C%20cardboard%2C%20textile%20plastic%2C%20wires%2C%20metals%20etc.%20Most%20of%20the%20waste%20is%20plastic%20waste%20which%20goes%20to%20a%20factory%20where%20it%20is%20converted%20into%20tiles.%20We%20have%20collaboration%20with%20recyclers%20where%20waste%20goes%20to%20and%20apparel%20companies%20that%20need%20waste%20materials%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzdZCvlvXE6%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insta